rucial to a president's legacy. "president obama was able to put several brilliant legal minds on the bench, who are much more likely to follow the law where it leads rather than accept the extreme conservative deregulatory agenda pushed by this case," she said.       appeals court hears high-stakes challenge to obama's clean power plan      
